divs: Sighting DetailsI and my family decided to go on a trip.We went to the lake,,sisko jezero,,and then we walked to the top of a hill.Then we saw two cyclers.My father asked them to stop to make a photo of his girl friend.She was also with us.I made first one photo and then after 13 seconds i made the other photo.Exactly i didn`t see it.We didn`t hear,fell,or see anything.But when i arived at home,i was looking my photos on the computer and i saw the ufo.The place where i photographed is called ,,jelenak,, it`s on yhe mountain range bjelasica.I felt lucky to pothograph an ufo.That was my dream and it came true.After a year i photographed an other ufo,i will send the photo in the other report.
